::Grimmler::

"No problem," Grimmler says, making his way to the Maximal city and
walking to the CR chambers. He puts Firedrill in one and sets
Cliffjumper down.

"You should get repaired too," he says to Cliffjumper, already on his
way to the exit of Maximal City.
